AN alleged goat thief’s luck ran out when he managed to
flee the angry mob hoping to moer him, but dove into a croc infested river instead.According to Nyasa
Times, Shadreck Vitto (23) had been in hiding for three days earlier last
week after apparently stealing four goats in his village in Chikwawa, southern
Malawi.But on Wednesday, he was spotted by residents in Lazaro
